      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·王風·010.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">丘中有麻.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>丘中有麻，彼留子嗟。彼留子嗟，將其來施施。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the mound where is the hemp,
Some one is detaining Zijie.
Some one is there detaining Zijie; -
Would that he would come jauntily [to me]!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
