      <prop type="x-translation-ref">丘中有麻.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>丘中有麥，彼留子國。彼留子國，將其來食。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the mound where is the wheat,
Some one is detaining Ziguo.
Some one is there detaining Ziguo; -
Would that he would come and eat with me!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
