      <prop type="x-translation-ref">丘中有麻.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>丘中有李，彼留之子。彼留之子，貽我佩玖。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the mound where are the plum trees,
Some one is detaining those youths.
Some one is there detaining those youths; -
They will give me Jiu-stones for my girdle.</seg>
      </tuv>
